A function that accepts a callback with some parameters may be written with the parameters
of the callback as parameters of the original calling function.

frontmatter.shortDescription: Parameters of a callback function may be written as parameters of the caller function
frontmatter.shortCorrection: A function that expects a callback has that callback function as a parameter
